rbit</a> <!-- -->installed</p><p>2. Plug in your Android phone to this computer</p><p>3. Ensure your Android phone is the selected device in Orbit:</p><img alt="Select your Android device in Orbit" loading="lazy" width="760" height="230" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="mx-auto my-4 w-4/5 rounded-lg" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.expo.dev%2Fstatic%2Fimages%2Fgo%2Forbit-android-device.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.expo.dev%2Fstatic%2Fimages%2Fgo%2Forbit-android-device.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.expo.dev%2Fstatic%2Fimages%2Fgo%2Forbit-android-device.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75"/><p class="mb-2">4. Start the Expo Go app download:</p></div><button class="cursor-pointer inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-solid font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition h-9 rounded-[calc(9*4px)] px-4 text-sm border-button-primary bg-button-primary text-button-primary active:scale-98 hocus:bg-button-primary-hover relative" data-testid="artifact-orbit-button" type="button"><svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="translate-z shrink-0 icon-sm text-palette-white" role="img"><g id="orbit-custom-icon"><g id="Group 1197147278"><g id="Union"><path fill="currentColor" d="M11.636 4.55029C14.1571 4.55045 16.3858 5.80322 17.7335 7.71641C17.7485 7.73773 17.7621 7.75965 17.7746 7.78189C18.9664 7.65968 20.0224 7.6462 20.8444 7.74354C21.3036 7.79794 21.7331 7.89179 22.0818 8.04752C22.4092 8.19382 22.8247 8.46867 22.9592 8.9707C23.0649 9.36574 22.9491 9.72613 22.7964 9.99209C22.6452 10.2555 22.422 10.4927 22.1801 10.7029C21.6934 11.1257 20.9908 11.5583 20.1541 11.9816C19.7771 12.1723 19.316 12.0209 19.1252 11.6439C18.9348 11.267 19.086 10.8066 19.4629 10.616C20.2542 10.2156 20.8294 9.85107 21.1774 9.54874C21.2419 9.49264 21.2927 9.44093 21.3345 9.39722C21.1801 9.34625 20.9594 9.29743 20.6648 9.26253C19.9033 9.17234 18.8107 9.19247 17.4968 9.35326C17.1083 9.4007 16.7525 9.148